author: Madeline Roth
title: Alesso And Liam Payne Talk Uplifting ‘Midnight’ Video, Self-Isolation, And Fan Remixes
description: Alesso and Liam Payne tell MTV News about their new single, "Midnight," and its accompanying video, which they made while in quarantine last month.
content:
Alesso and Liam Payne are on the phone, but before we can start talking about their new single, we need to determine what day of the week it is.
